rows.label: tlk4140002801_msg0001
rows.name:
You helped us back in Gula...
Thank you. We'd never have been
able to come here without your help.

rows.label: tlk4140002801_msg0002
rows.name:
As for Da...what's done is done.
So I'd rather not think about how
he's going to take it.

rows.label: tlk4140002801_msg0003
rows.name:
I do feel bad for leaving Ma on her
own, though...

rows.label: tlk4140002801_msg0004
rows.name:
But I'm happy. Everything's new and
different to me here, but as long as I've
got Norman, I'm not afraid.
